text: Woden Valley Rams Rugby League Club is an Australian rugby league football club based in Woden, Australian Capital Territory formed in 1967.http://juniors.wodenvalleyrams.com/club- information/http://www.canberratimes.com.au/sport/act-sport/woden-valley-rams- go-down-fighting-against-powerhouse-queanbeyan-blues-20150419-1mo7m1.html In 2018, the Rams won their first premiership since 1996 beating the Tuggeranong Bushrangers 31-30. ==Notable juniors== *Nigel Gaffey (1989-00 Canberra Raiders, Sydney Roosters & Penrith Panthers) *David Cox (1995-99 Canberra Raiders & Illawarra Steelers) *Luke Priddis (1997-10 Canberra Raiders, Brisbane Broncos, Penrith Panthers & St George Illawarra Dragons) *Lincoln Withers (2000-13 Canberra Raiders, Wests Tigers, St George Illawarra Dragons & Hull F.C.) *Brenton Lawrence (2011- Gold Coast Titans & Manly Sea Eagles) *Sami Sauiluma (2013- Canberra Raiders, Cronulla Sharks & Gold Coast Titans) *Bailey Simonsson (2018- Canberra Raiders) ==References== ==External links== * * Category:Sporting clubs in Canberra Category:Rugby league teams in the Australian Capital Territory Category:Rugby clubs established in 1967 Category:1967 establishments in Australia
